subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: The Scarlet Knights were ousted Sunday night in the semifinals of the Oklahoma City Regional by Purdue, a team that had flown under the radar in the tournament.
